CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: TMD Energy is principally involved in marine fuel bunkering services specializing in the supply and marketing of marine gas oil and marine fuel oil which include high sulfur fuel oil, low sulfur fuel oil and very low sulfur fuel oil, to ships and vessels at sea. We are also involved in the provision of ship management services for in-house and external vessels, as well as vessel chartering. We operate in 19 ports across Malaysia, and we operate under a fleet of 15 bunkering vessels to provide STS transfer of marine fuels.
